name: libExperiment
tagline: Code Written To Experiment With Various Techniques And Otherwise Not Very Useful...
body:
### Welcome to libExperiment

This project is code written to experiment with various techniques. As such, it is not generally useful except as example code.

Please see the [documentation](doc/) for more information.

### Authors and Contributors

The author is Jonathan Seng (@nekenyu).

There are currently no other contributors.

### Documentation

Documentation can be found in [doc/](doc/).
